To measure the ROI of Rox, she began piloting it with a few reps on her tea=
m, and =E2=80=9Cstarted to see ROI from those reps, so I piloted giving the=
m larger books, then I piloted the new double role using Rox.=E2=80=9D Not =
only did it work, =E2=80=9CMy reps were asking me, =E2=80=98How early are t=
hese guys? Can I invest?=E2=80=99=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
If reps are more efficient with Rox =E2=80=93 can spend more time building =
