Letting anyone sign up and test a product like Rox=E2=80=99s this early is,=
 as Jonathan Haas put, =E2=80=9Cthe strongest endorsement of their confiden=
ce in this product as anything,=E2=80=9D because it means fully exposing th=
e product to the public instead of a small group of partners, putting a ton=
