e, though, was due to a much more specific reason than most people realize:=
 SMBs were a perfect first customer because, with lower spend volumes, they=
 weren&#8217;t as sensitive to take rates as Adyen&#8217;s larger customers=
, which meant Stripe has always had a higher average take rate.&nbsp;</p><p=
 style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-=
