offsite next week,&#8221; she said. &#8220;He already did that once a month=
 ago.&#8221;&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55)=
;line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;"><span>If the long game is to collect t=
