;s vision is instructive in determining what the future might look like if =
Rox succeeds.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55=
);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;"><span>To that end, there&#8217;s anot=
her 40% stat that I&#8217;ve been saving. When we first spoke, Ishan pointe=
d out that </span><strong>&#8220;40% of business spend is GTM.&#8221;</stro=
ng><span> It is a huge chunk of the global economy.&nbsp;</span></p><p styl=
e=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size:=
 16px;">Rhetorically, he asked, &#8220;Can they be 5-10% more efficient? Ca=
n we return 5-10% savings to the CEO and the CEO.&#8221;&nbsp;</p><p style=
=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: =
16px;"><span>Confidently, he answered, &#8220;I&#8217;ve done that, twice, =
at scale, </span><em>without</em><span> a fully built-out system like Rox.&=
#8221;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55=
);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">With Rox, he thinks, the efficiency g=
ains will be more dramatic. Smaller teams, more revenue, higher margins. Gr=
unt work: eliminated. Human touch: elevated.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"margin: 0=
 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">This i=
s where I started asking him questions like, &#8220;What are we all going t=
o do with ourselves in the future?&#8221; And, &#8220;Will all sales just b=
e bot-to-bot.&#8221;&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,=
 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;"><span>Some of it will be, he t=
hinks, but there will be human winners, those with the &#8220;</span><stron=
g>creative force</strong><span>.&#8221;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=3D"margin:=
