t that good yet, is just to earn the data and integrations, to become the s=
ystem of record. Over the next year, he wants to save sellers 20 to 30 hour=
s every week while making them 50% more effective.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=
=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: =
16px;"><span>But that&#8217;s not the </span><em>ultimate </em><span>goal.&=
nbsp;</span></p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-=
